com.alexgilleran.icesoap.observer
Interface SOAPObserver<ReturnType,SOAPFaultType>

Type Parameters:
ReturnType - The type of the object that will be retrieved from this request.
SOAPFaultType - The type of the class to use for SOAPFaults
All Known Subinterfaces:
SOAP11ListObserver<ReturnType>, SOAP11Observer<ReturnType>, SOAPListObserver<ReturnType,SOAPFaultType>
public interface SOAPObserver<ReturnType,SOAPFaultType>

Used to receive events from a running SOAP Request on the Android UI thread.
